quran[5{c,v,t}:
3,149,momino! agar tum kafiroon ka kaha maan lau ge to woh tum ko ultay paon phair kar ( murtid kar ) den ge phir tum barray khasaray mein par jao ge
3,150,( yeh tumahray madadgaar nahi hain ) balkay khuda tumhara madadgaar hai aur woh sab se behtar madadgaar hai
3,151,hum anqareeb kafiroon ke dilon mein tumhara roab bitha den ge kyunkay yeh khuda ke sath shirk karte hain jis ki is ne koi bhi Daleel nazil nahi ki aur un ka thikana dozakh hai woh zaalmon ka bohat bُra thikana hai
3,152,aur khuda ne apna wada sacha kar diya ( yani ) is waqt jabkay tum kafiroon ko is ke hukum se qatal kar rahay they yahan taq ke jo tum chahtay they khuda ne tum ko dikha diya is ke baad tum ne himmat haar di aur hukum ( paighambar ) mein jhagra karne lagey aur is ki nafarmani ki baaz to tum mein se duniya ke khawastgah they aur baaz akhirat ke taalib is waqt khuda ne tum ko un ( ke muqablay ) se phair ( kar bhaga ) diya taakay tumhari azmaish kere aur is ne tumhara qasoor maaf kar diya aur khuda momino par bara fazl karne wala hai
3,153,( woh waqt bhi yaad karne ke Laiq hai ) jab tum log daur bhage jatay they aur kisi ko peechay phir kar nahi dekhte they aur rasool allah tum ko tumahray peechay kharray bulaa rahay they to khuda ne tum ko gham par gham pohanchaya taakay jo cheez tumahray haath se jati rahi ya jo museebat tum par waqay hui hai is se tum andoh naak nah ho aur khuda tumahray sab aamaal se khabardaar hai
